  <brief_title>Use of Local Infiltration Analgesia Following Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Local Infiltration Analgesia in Total Hip Arthroplasty - Efficacy of Multiple Bolus Injections With Ropivacaine and Ketorolac</official_title>
